“Elite” Would Like to Access Your Photos - Allow photo access to add photos to your profile.
“Elite” Would Like to Access the Camera - Allow access to the camera to take photos for your profile.
“Elite” Would Like to Access the Microphone - Allow access to the microphone to upload audio to your profile.
“Elite” Would Like to Access Your location - Allow access to the location in the background to discover people in your area in real-time.
